tool_description: The Email Temporary Generator API generates temporary email addresses that can be used to protect the privacy and avoid spam. This API is easy to use and can be integrated with any application. Users can create temporary email addresses and check their inboxes to view incoming emails.
title: Email Temporary Generator

api_list.name: Inbox
api_list.description: Get your email messages of that specific temp email.

api_list.name: Create Temp Email
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://email-temporary-generator.p.rapidapi.com/inbox/create"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "email-temporary-generator.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
